Title: Daily Driving a Smartphone Without Screen
Description:
Last year my phone’s screen broke in a way, that made it
                register inputs even if nothing was touching it. Any reasonable
                person would simply get a new phone, but I am not reasonable
                and also didn’t have any spare cash back then. So here is
                a short post about how I used my phone without a screen for
                around a month.
